Suggested commands:


    snakk extract <file> [ -o <output-file> ]

Extracts the body of the message file.


    snakk header <file>
    	[ -o <output-file> ]
    	[ -f | --format= { verbatim | fold | unfold | bash } ]

Extracts the header of the message file, verbatim by default.


    snakk envelope <file> [ -o <output-file> ] [ -i <header-file> ]

Prepends headers to the file.